lead_paragraph: Leicester City boss Claudio Ranieri has urged his players to forget their fairytale run to the Premier League title last season and be wary of dropping into the relegation zone in this campaign.

headline.print_headline: Ranieri Demands Leicester Focus on the Present Not Past
headline.main: Ranieri Demands Leicester Focus on the Present Not Past
